1. Molim te da mi oprostiš, *milosti* tvojoj. (Please forgive me, *by your mercy*.)
2. Nije mi dao *milost* ni za trenutak. (He didn't give me *mercy* for a moment.)
3. *Milost* Božja, pomiluj nas grešne. (God's *mercy*, have mercy on us sinners.)
4. Ovo delo je izuzetno *milosno*. (This work is exceptionally *gracious*.)
5. Molim vas da mi ukažete na *milost*. (Please show me *mercy*.)
6. Oni su živeli u *milosti* i blagostanju. (They lived in *grace* and prosperity.)
7. Nije imao srca da mu ne ukaže *milosti*. (He didn't have the heart to deny him *mercy*.)
8. *Milostinja* je važan deo hrišćanske tradicije. (Almsgiving is an important part of the Christian tradition.)
9. Učitelj je pokazao *milost* prema učeniku koji je bio bolestan. (The teacher showed *kindness* to the student who was sick.)
10. *Milost* je vrlina koju treba negovati. (Mercy is a virtue that needs to be nurtured.)